{"tid":749834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「銀髮族2025」商機來臨？中國7年後老年人料達3億","createTime":"2018-07-20T10:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T12:35:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5a83cb4b9218ac266e0682ebf01701eb0ace06","tid":749834,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T10:57:05.000Z","msg":"07月19日(四) 21:14   <br />\n(Getty Images圖片)<br />\n(Getty Images圖片)<br />\n中國傳媒報道，到了2050年，老年人或將佔總人口逾三分之一！國家衛生健康委員會表示，預計到2050年前後，老年人口數目將達到高峰的4.87億人，佔總人口約34.9%。 <br />\n<br />\n若拉近一點看，預計到2025年，60歲及以上老年人口數目將達到3億，佔總人口約五分之一；到2033年將突破4億，約佔總人口的四分之一。 <br />\n－－－－－－ <br />\n《骰寶坊》誠邀各地【賭王】【賭后】挑戰神人境界，每日更有百萬籌碼等你領取！ <br />\n立即免費下載，體驗《骰寶坊》最真實、刺激的多人在線骰寶遊戲！"},{"pid":"39087475efc837662b81690dcf0aa9c40965bf16","tid":749834,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T11:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食住花生等睇戲"},{"pid":"c9482388eae93c62bb21af9c95f199c1d48f9086","tid":749834,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T11:08:06.000Z","msg":"呃廢老既商機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港已經玩緊,日日大把廢老排隊畀人呃<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"656901060939ff8f077d66911ddebf65ac3a2d45","tid":749834,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T11:27:17.000Z","msg":"中国銀髮2025<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" c